high_descs: Go forward, turn right at the fridge, go forward, turn right at the table
Pick up the egg on the table
Turn right, go forward, turn right at the fridge
Put the egg in the fridge, wait, pick up the egg from the fridge
Turn around, go forward a bit, turn left, go forward a bit, turn left in front of the microwave
Put the egg in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Cool an egg and put it into microwave

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the fridge. Make a right and walk forward. Turn right again to face the counter.
Pick up the egg off of the counter.
Turn to the right then walk forward. Turn to the right again and face the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the egg inside. Chill the egg then take it out.
Turn to the left and move forward. Face the microwave.
Place the egg inside the microwave and shut it.
anns.task_desc: Chill an egg and place in microwave.

high_descs: Walk to the dining table on the egg's side.
Grab the egg from the table.
Walk to the front of the fridge.
Chill the egg by placing it in the fridge, then grab it.
Go to the microwave next to the fridge.
Place the egg in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Chill an egg and place it in the microwave.
